sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_include_9db087842fd2d5101729b8e72799b675
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.ageScript</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>ageScript</name><script><![CDATA[var ageScript = Class.create();
ageScript.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
    checkAge: function() {
        var dob = this.getParameter('sysparam_id'); //param from client script
        var today = new GlideDateTime();
        var todayYear = today.getYearLocalTime();
        var bday = new GlideDateTime(dob.toString());
        var bdayYear = bday.getYearLocalTime();
        var age = todayYear - bdayYear;
        return age;
